text: Sibogasyrinx is a genus of sea snails, marine gastropod mollusks in the family Cochlespiridae.Bouchet, P. (2015). Sibogasyrinx. In: MolluscaBase (2015). Accessed through: World Register of Marine Species at http://www.marinespecies.org/aphia.php?p=taxdetails&id;=578099 on 2016-07-19 Previously it was considered a subgenus of Leucosyrinx Dall, 1889 in the family Pseudomelatomidae.. ==Species== Species within the genus Sibogasyrinx include: * Sibogasyrinx archibenthalis (Powell, 1969) * Sibogasyrinx pyramidalis (Schepman, 1913) * Sibogasyrinx sangeri Kantor, Fedosov & Puillandre, 2018 ==References== ==External links==
